Author: organicco
Title: [ANN][ICO][AIRDROP] ORGANICCO GREEN-TECH PROVEN TECHNOLOGY
Body: Good Morning All Wishing you a happy Thursday As always we are working extremely hard and continuing to develop Organicco.  We have signed an NDA with London based Asset Fund Management company to give exclusive access to raise fund on our behalf..  We are now well on the way to putting a structure together for developing biofuel plant in order to access the allocated fund.  We are in discussion with a large fertiliser distributor and aiming to get an off-take contract agreed with them which will create another opportunity to fund UK fertiliser plant project development.  More updates will follow soon.  Enjoy the day

Author: organicco
Title: [ANN][ICO][AIRDROP] ORGANICCO GREEN-TECH PROVEN TECHNOLOGY
Body: Good Morning and Wishing you all a happy Friday This week we made a good progress.. Most of complaints regarding token allocation have been resolved..  We signed an NDA with London based Asset Management Company to raise the project funds to develop three organic fertiliser plants..  We have signed three way collaborative agreement for biofuel project. Now working out the structure on it.  We are awaiting result for the application made for government fund for UK/ Canada collaboration. we will know the result end of this month.. It’s a tough competition and if we are successful, it will give us a good boost.  We have applied for pre-qualification for Enterprise Investment Scheme (EIS) which gives up to 50% tax relief for UK investors who invest in our business. Almost 80% of the capital is protected by the government.  We have a strong candidate willing to join us as Chief Financial Officer (CFO), which will be crucial for further business development.  Now UK is committing to net zero carbon emission by 2050, the green tech industry is a growing industry. It is worth more than £1 trillion in UK alone, a huge potential to go after, we are concentrating on $1.2 trillion worldwide industry sector. After all we all have to eat for survival.  Some councillors are asking for our company when they consider attending exhibition too.. exciting times ahead  More updates to follow..  We thank you for all those who believe in our project..

Author: organicco
Title: [ANN][ICO][AIRDROP] ORGANICCO GREEN-TECH PROVEN TECHNOLOGY
Body: Hi, Thank you for an excellent question and comments.. indeed many have said this to us, and in fact even suggested why would you make such a statement, some even say the things we are saying are illegal. It is because many are aiming to raise funds with no risk to them apart from the investors like yourself.. so far a lot had been invested on just ideas.. not sure about Moneypot or any others who have given guarantees in the past, I am sure that is just another digital platform idea!  We have a fully working units, and delivered projects successfully in different parts of the world and invested our own personal funds which is over £2 million over 10 year period.. but as with any growing business we lack support from bank and other sources of funding. Since we have ready to develop projects, with planning and permits, your investments will be carefully invested in these projects.  Once a project is delivered, subjected to how quickly we raise the necessary fund, we can complete the project before our tokens are even listed on exchanges. At that time, we can refinance the systems that we delivered and we will have the funds available if anyone wishes to pull out.    Also, we are looking for long term investors.. most of the current crypto investors are short term with small amount and wanting to get huge return quickly.. which is basically gambling, and addictive. Therefore they are less likely to invest early. For that reason, we are doing private sales, by having face to face meetings and Q&A sessions and raising funds at our own pace. We are also offering managed fund services to those who have no idea about crypto currencies and ICO. Mainly those are the ones benefiting from capital guarantees.  We are confident, even before majority of the crowd start investing, we would have met our soft cap.. so keep following us, and you will learn more about us.. and also please keep challenging us, that is how we can improve.

In the past, many said our technology is too good to be true, and we proved them wrong by having systems now working for many years now.  The blockchain is new technology and here to stay and will be changing many things in future. As we are innovating team, we em race new technologies. We have good use for blockchain technology (please check an answer for another similar question on this thread). Since we trade internationally, which comes with huge costs from getting letter of credit, insurance, factoring, performance guarantees, etc, our easiPAYER solution solves it. We then want all our clients and suppliers to use them too, again reducing banking fees, corruptions, and giving real benefits to farmers.  Our ultimate goal is to form first international cooperative for farming, and imagine the benefits small farmers will receive from the blockchain technologies, where we will continue to develop many things, such as keeping records of batch production giving complete transparency of where your food come from (do you know your origin of food)?

Author: organicco
Title: [ANN][ICO][AIRDROP] ORGANICCO GREEN-TECH PROVEN TECHNOLOGY
Body: The blockchain talks directly with our investors. Whereas shares only talks through meetings, publications, documents - there is no direct relationship with the people who are investing in us. We want our valued investors to be involved too, and they can help sell our products and services, take our technologies to various countries - give feedbacks on improvements, and what we can do better to keep ahead of others..  The reason I did not get involved with bitcoin in the early days, due to its affiliations with wrong stuffs.. but on discovering the blockchain technology, I believe there are many more benefits to be had, which including getting rid of corruptions.. hence our services are direct.. there's is no middlemen taking the benefits.. it is our investors benefits.  Once the scams, shillings, hypes are fixed and people get real deals on investment opportunities - then the blockchain technology will evolve to change the future of many things.. it is bringing the true power of people through internet! so we do not want to be miss out on it.. There is still a small element of who is popular wins - but it may improve over time.  Finally, we want to be part of getting everything regulated on the blockchain area, so getting involved early also makes lots of commercial sense. Hence for us, timing is perfect!

Author: organicco
Title: [ANN][ICO][AIRDROP] ORGANICCO GREEN-TECH PROVEN TECHNOLOGY
Body: We have broad range of markets: for example, we are adding value to many large companies, such as paper-mill, waste water treatment facilities, farming, etc which many young children do not understand (I heard once a primary school child, when asked, said the chicken comes from supermarkets!)..  We want to provide cost effective energy to developing countries, so that they also have the access to basic utilities in life.  There are governments who can reduce taxes with our system (which is not very popular - as they prefer to have the tax as constant revenue, and instead invest the savings on other projects).  Basically, we all need food to survive, so any source of it is our opportunity! But currently focused on few key and profitable industries. I was told by Paul Herrback, who is an ex-mayor of one of the municipals in Montreal, that he will have around $100 millon opportunity by end of this year even without the success of our ICO. It comes from 13 years of hard work.

Author: organicco
Title: [ANN][ICO][AIRDROP] ORGANICCO GREEN-TECH PROVEN TECHNOLOGY
Body: Hello John,  Thank you for your kind wishes. I understand we have not clearly defined the business ecosystem and lack more information of our team. We will be adding more details on them, some of it will be added to the major revision of our white paper.  In the meantime, our ecosystem in brief:  Customers: Our customers, as you gather from our website, under clients such as Boxford Suffolk Farm (bought ecoDRYER), Oakland Farm (bought ecoHERO) are in farming. Then we have MRC (bought ecoHERO), which is government/municipality. Another example is Biowaste Recovery Ltd (bought ecoDRYER), who is a waste management company, Loc Troi is one of the largest private company in Vietnam who has 45,000 farmers in their portfolio who bought our fertiliser plant and Bangladesh Agriculture Research Institute (BARI) bought a pilot unit from us. We have food manufacturers such as KVeg is using our system.  Therefore, our clients can come from several sectors - since 'food' is fundamental for our existence. Probably many of you are not aware of how insecure our future food supplies are. It is one of the reason we are working so hard to do what we can for the future of our children. I hope you can help spread the word!  markets: The global industrial waste management market alone is worth around $1,442 Billion. The UK Organic/ Food Waste industry is worth around £500 million and only around 18% of its value is realised by the few waste management operators existing in UK.  products:   we have well developed products, such as ecoHERO which converts organic materials into fertiliser, animal feed or biomass fuel. Then we have ecoDRYER, which is similar to ecoHERO but does only part of its work mainly aimed at renewable energy industry. We will be launching ecoREDUCER for reducing costs of waste management, and producing biomass fuel. Then there are other products, such as ecoMAN and ecoENERGY for producing renewable energy and renewable fuel.  regulations: we are working hard to be ahead of any regulatory changes, in somes ways driving it. We are already talking with US SEC, in UK with FCA and Cifas then to work with FINMA in Switzerland, etc.. these are hard work, but we will do them.  if you are talking about ecosystem of business evolution:  birth: our company is already formed, invested more than £2 million. We have good suppliers and experienced work force. We have clients and on the verge of signing large value contracts. In order to deliver them effectively, we need to be properly set up and sufficiently funded.  expansion: we are at the point of expansion, hence doing this ICO. If enough people know about us, and enough people invest on us, we certainly grow a healthier business.  leadership: again this is where expansion comes in to effect. We already have good discounts with some key suppliers such as Siemens. We are offering cost reduction and adding value to our clients. Therefore, we are in prime position to become the one of the leader in our industry (as no-one is currently dominating).  We have good leaders in our team. For example, Paul Herrbach is an ex-mayor of a municipal in Montreal and Vipul Patel is a chartered accountant. We have good visions, and able to inspire and empower the people who work for Organicco.  innovation: Organicco is a company encourages innovation, which is the key part of our business progress. It is why we have several innovative technology developments on plan, such as prodcuing renewable energy, renewable fuel from farm waste as well as forming world wide cooperation for 'good food production'. Helping farmers with technology, knowledge, and finance too as one farmer in UK commit suicide a week. That is 52 farmers lost a year. Similar story in many countries. If it continues, who is going to produce our food in future?

Title: [ANN][ICO][AIRDROP] ORGANICCO GREEN-TECH PROVEN TECHNOLOGY
Body: Not sure what do you mean by 'project':  If you meant the ICO, we are currently working on it. This is a new area for us, we are learning fast. Bringing in some experts to help us with it too. But some are just ridiculously expensive, in this hyped up world the reality is somewhat cloudy. Therefore, we are working directly with regulators then engage suitably qualified personal at relevant time. This will always be work in progress. As regulations changes, we will accommodate those changes in our business operations.  So currently working on FCA and Cifas in UK and US SEC. We have plan to work on FINMA depending if any participants from Switzerland.  If you are talking our 'project' such as fertiliser plants developments etc, then of course we meet relevant country regulatory requirements. We always work with regulators, to meet whatever is required. After all they are there to help all of us to have a level playing field and protect consumer in us, and also the vulnerability in us.  With our product development, we have to meet several health and safety protocols such CE, EC, CSA, UL, standards. We have delivered systems to UK, Canada, Malaysia, Vietnam, Bangladesh and Nigeria.

Author: organicco
Title: [ANN][ICO][AIRDROP] ORGANICCO GREEN-TECH PROVEN TECHNOLOGY

Please note that we have three large projects are ready to be developed - our technology already is proven (please visit the YouTube channel for few video's of system working https://www.youtube.com/channel/UCPfAUtJt8G_VzQYOYlZlxMQ). Indeed the market will fluctuate, it is why we are offering the guarantee for those who support us in the early days.  Also, remember, our easiPayer tokens will not be listed on any of the exchanges - instead, it will be independently valued (which will be equivalent, in some cases better than, fiat currency). So market fluctuation cannot affect its valuation. easiPayer tokens are not sold as part of ICO, only the Organicco Tokens are - so these two tokens must not be confused.  At worst case scenario, we can refinance our projects and recover the initial investment. For these reasons we are looking for long term investors.  With regards to regulators, we already started talking to US SEC and in the process of applying for exemption. We are in discussion with UK FCA too, whilst ensuring we are working on obtaining suitable insurance cover for our activities too. There are handful of people have done crypto bonds and escrow types of coin. We believe this is the time for change, where the ICO is done properly rather than some hype and gamble.  There are always risks, what we are aiming to achieve is to better manage them!

Title: [ANN][ICO][AIRDROP] ORGANICCO GREEN-TECH PROVEN TECHNOLOGY
Body: Excellent question: indeed, we have many years of expertise in managing organic waste material. Our mission is to become one of the leading companies in the world to provide comprehensive solution for organic waste. Mainly the project is defined by the budget and of course its return on investment. We have experience of converting organic waste into fertiliser, animal feed, renewable energy and renewable fuel.  We already have installed number of fertiliser plants, we are installing one small unit for producing animal feed, we are part way through building a small unit for producing biomass fuel,  we are working on renewable fuel plants (awaiting private investment for it) and we will be launching a new technology for renewable energy solution that is affordable mainly for developing countries where this type of energy sources are more important.

About Organicco The Organic Technology Ltd was set up in January 2017, by the team who for over 10 years, developed a number of green technologies for transforming unwanted organic materials into useful saleable products. In addition to creating demands for these technologies, they also generated markets for these natural capitals. We are the only company in the world who delivers technology to solve problems but who also purchase the by-products. It is our unique point. Initially we have used subcontractors to deliver projects, but experienced problems of reliability which eroded our profitability. As a result, we decided to open a manufacturing division to produce and deliver high quality products directly to clients.  our mission To maintain long lasting relationship with our clients  To continually add or improve features to our range of products  To continually establish and maintain the position as a leading provider of technology for creating natural capitals from unwanted organics   our vision As Organicco we aim to be on the right side of current and future regulations. Our objective is to deliver a good return for our investors whilst managing its risks to best possible standards.  We are continuously striving to delivery best products and solutions at good value for our clients.  Our goal is making arable farming more environmentally friendly, and support natural food production with better yield. We want to help overturn heavy use of chemical fertiliser that cause soil erosion and ground water pollution.  We believe there is no waste in nature, hence our aim is to eradicate organic 'waste' , and convert them into useful products with no or very little by-product in the most environmentally friendly manner possible.

The UK Organic/ Food Waste industry is valued at approximately £500 million of which only 18% is realised by the few waste management operators existing in the UK. Consequently, there are wasted opportunities and these need to be tackled. If current rates of soil degradation continues all of the world’s top soil could be gone within 60 years. This is caused by extensive farming methods including the use of chemicals and pesticides. This is a problem that urgently needs addressing and  converting unwanted organic materials into organic fertiliser helps prevent this effect and create a naturally closed loop cycle.  Payment in the export market: Letter of credit and insurance costs are very high and takes time to setup. Additionally, payment is made when goods are delivered, which can be a problem if there is no Letter of Credit. This creates a high risk of none payment. Moreover, conventional banking and even FX trading takes time, and comes with a cost and additional risks. We aim to eradicate such problems through our easiPayer Technology, the full details of which will be explored later.  SOLUTIONS ______________   By developing green tech projects, we will be creating a closed loop economy from natural capitals. These natural capitals will return the investment typically in less than four years, whilst each project will continue to produce revenue for more than 20 years.  easiPayer - A Low cost international payment platform designed to replace letter of credits and invoice factoring that is fast, safe and easy to use.  HOW IT WORKS ______________   Focused primarily on green technology related products, the funds raised will be used to develop projects via our subsidiary companies to create natural capitals such as organic fertilisers for food production, animal feed, biomass fuel, renewable energy and renewable fuels:     •   produce these natural capitals using our patented technologies to generate a continuous cash-flow which in turn will be used to repay the capital investment with interest. Our ultimate goal is to play a major role in the worldwide production of food using sustainable and environmentally friendly methods and in the production of renewable energy and renewable fuel.     •   develop several projects in the green and agri-tech industries in the UK, Canada and South East Asia.     •   loan our associated companies to develop these  projects using green technology solutions called ecoHERO and ecoDRYER, which produce organic fertiliser and animal feed from unwanted commercial organic materials.     •   produce small quantity biomass fuels from mixed waste materials using yet another of our technology solutions, ecoREDUCER. Finally, we will be producing renewable energy and renewable fuels, from unwanted organic materials.     •   create a low cost and fast international payment platform based on blockchain technology, called easiPayer:           + The easiPayer token is valued with real assets by independent auditors, which fixes the value at the time of purchase. The client allocates these tokens towards the purchase of the fertiliser and this authori-sation cannot be withdrawn. This provides us with the comfort that the client has sufficient funds to trade and he can only refuse the product based on poor quality or insufficient volume. + If there should be a dispute it will be referred to an independent ombudsman and will aim to have a resolution within 28 days. + Through this platform other terms of payment can be agreed, for example stage payments. + Provision of fiat currencies: We will ensure that easiPayer tokens can easily be traded for fiat currency. This will be done through conventional banking systems. + Transaction fees: We will be charging a very small transaction fee of 0.50% + mining fee. We will also charge 1.5% for trading easiPayer tokens for fiat currency. + Potential revenue: Assuming 74% of £10 million is traded at 0.50% this will return £13.4 million revenue per year. 50% exchanged at 1.5% will return £27.3 million per year. Therefore, the potential total revenue from easiPayer transactions is around c.£41 million per year. This revenue can only can grow by creating more asset backed coins that are independently audited. Author: organicco
Title: [ANN][ICO][AIRDROP] ORGANICCO GREEN-TECH PROVEN TECHNOLOGY
Body: Hello Kikurin, indeed the funds raised by ICO is used for two main purposes. In many ways it is like ETF but with added advantage of cryptocurrency.  The first part is developing green-tech projects using proven and patented technology. Again these are assets, which can be refinanced once the project is fully developed.  The second part is for developing blockchain based international payment platform which is called easiPayer, where we will be holding 25% of the raised fund in the form of various assets, such as real estates, gold, bond, silver, etc. The reason for it is every easiPayer coin released will be equivalent to independent valuation (which will be published for public scrutiny). Most importantly it will not be listed on any exchanges and generate income through its transaction fees. The only purpose is to make internation payment much easier, than letter of credit, factoring, etc, hence some call it like an digital escrow platform.
